<h1>Topics and Activities</h1>

<div class="text">
	
<p>
VIEW currently supports four different types of activities
for a number of grammar topics.
</p>

<ol>
<li>The <em>Colorize</em> activity is a form of receptive presentation. It highlights the 
targeted linguistic forms in the text.</li>
<li><em>Click</em> is an activity that requests the user to do productive representation
by clicking on the targeted forms.</li>
<li><em>Multiple Choice</em> asks the user to choose the target from a list with distractors.</li>
<li>The <em>Practice</em> activity offers fill-in-the-blank and editing exercises.</li>
</ol>

<p>
Choose a topic from the menu to on the left to learn more about its activities.
</p>

</div>
